BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 123 Tm (Why it is used:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 70 97 Tm (- raw word IDs are not meaningful enough) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 70 79 Tm (- embedding converts them into dense vector representations) Tj ET
